## Erotic Mood System — Romantic Pool

erotic-moods-category-romantic = Romantic Moods

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-handholding-name = Handholding
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-handholding-desc = Reach for someone's hand, you need the intimacy of the touch.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-kissing-name = Kissing
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-kissing-desc = Find someone you want to kiss and kiss them properly — slowly, with your full attention on it.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-cuddling-name = Cuddling
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-cuddling-desc = Find somewhere comfortable and pull someone in close, or put yourself in a position to be pulled in.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-datenight-name = Dating
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-datenight-desc = Take someone somewhere nice for a proper time, or put out enough hints that someone takes you instead.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-loveletter-name = Love Letter
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-loveletter-desc = Write something down and give it to them. A paper, a fax, a nanochat, whatever's to hand — just say it properly.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-morningafter-name = Aftercare
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-morningafter-desc = Stay somewhere with someone a little longer than you need to, or ask someone to stay with you.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-sweetnothings-name = Sweet Nothings
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-sweetnothings-desc = Murmur something fond into some cutie's ear.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-slowdance-name = Slow Dancing
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-slowdance-desc = Ask someone to dance somewhere with a little space — keep swaying together until it means something.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-spoiled-name = Being Spoiled
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-spoiled-desc = Let someone know you'd like a small gift or a bit of fuss. Let them make it up to you, or make it up to someone else.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-pining-name = Pining
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-pining-desc = Be obvious about wanting someone without quite saying it — linger, brush past them, let the tension build.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-petnames-name = Pet Names
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-petnames-desc = Call someone something soft and specific that's just for them, or earn yourself a name like that.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-quietcompany-name = Quiet Company
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-quietcompany-desc = Sit down next to someone with nowhere to be and just stay there alongside them for a while.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-protective-name = Protective
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-protective-desc = Stay close to someone and make sure they're alright, or find someone who'll do the same for you.

hl-erotic-mood-romantic-casualaffection-name = Casual Affection
hl-erotic-mood-romantic-casualaffection-desc = Touch someone lightly as you pass — a hand on their arm, a bump of a shoulder. Mean it.
